platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Interact with machines to understand physics.
La physique et l'ingnierie, une machine  la fois.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Made with Tinybops usual charm and polish, Simple Machines distills difficult ideas into fun hands-on lessons. Spin giant screws, crack open icy boulders and use levers to bombard cartoon castlesall while learning about real-world physics.
